50|$|There {{are three}} ways {{to access the}} platform. There is a ramp down from the Browns Road Overbridge to the south <b>end</b> <b>of</b> the <b>platform.</b> There is a {{pedestrian}} level crossing from the park and ride carpark (which is on Dalgety Drive) to the south <b>end</b> <b>of</b> the <b>platform,</b> and there is another pedestrian level crossing from McVilly Road to the north <b>end</b> <b>of</b> the <b>platform.</b>|$|R
